summary = ["In Italy, Dini told reporters in the city of Trento that the government would decide Ocalan's request for asylum in a clear and responsible manner''but Ocalan has been absent from the battlefield for at least a month, and others contend that the PKK is capable of operating without him. Facing his first real foreign policy test, Prime Minister Massimo D'Alema must decide what to do with a prominent Kurdish rebel leader who was arrested at the Rome airport on Thursday"]